Package: covidscreen
Title: Simulate Asymptomatic Screening for COVID-19
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person('Jesse', 'Smith', email = 'Jesse.Smith@stjude.org', role = c('cre', 'aut')),
    person('Tomi',  'Mori',  email = 'Tomi.Mori@stjude.org',   role = 'aut'))
Description: The {covidscreen} package provides simple simulations
    for understanding the effects of assurance testing/screening
    on a population. It aims to help decision-makers determine whether and how
    to test for COVID-19 with limited resources.
